    4. RUN MOJITOO 

    MOJITOO_DM <- mojitoo_Matrix(
     reduction_matrix.list= list(RNA_PCA, ATAC_LSI),
     dims.list = list(1:50, 2:50) ## exclude 1st dimension of LSI
)
